  Violations:
  - Type: 1
    SubjectLine: Document inconsistency
    Description: Applicants are not allowed to provide documents containing false
      information (Face potrait on ID).
  - Type: 2
    SubjectLine: Invalid document
    Description: Applicant must provide documents that are government issued.
  - Type: 3
    SubjectLine: 'Incomplete document '
    Description: Applicant must provide complete documents.
  - Type: 5
    SubjectLine: Database absence
    Description: Applicants must be registered on the database.
  - Type: 6
    SubjectLine: Rejecting a hospitalized applicant
    Description: Applicants who just got discharged from the hospital must be accepted.
  - Type: 7
    SubjectLine: Rejecting a valid applicant
    Description: If the applicants meet the entry conditions, they should be accpeted.
